    Consider the Three Threes Clock Face in <xref ref="fig-three-threes"/>. Verify that each number on the clock face is represented correctly using three threes. Think about how you are using the Order of Operations to check each expression. Use your creativity to find as many expressions for each number as you can. 
    </p>

